import {NavLink} from 'react-router-dom';

import Main from '../layouts/main'
import Subnavigation from '../layouts/subnavigation'
import Header from '../layouts/header'
import Body from '../layouts/body'
import '../styles/theme.css'

const Services = ({className}) => (
  <Main className={className}>
    <Subnavigation title='Services'>
      <NavLink to='/services/frontend'>Frontend</NavLink>
      <NavLink to='/services/backend'>Backend</NavLink>
      <NavLink to='/services/mobile'>Mobile</NavLink>
    </Subnavigation>
    <Header title='Services'>Button</Header>
    <Body>Testing services body</Body>
  </Main>
);

export default Services;
